Hiding place
The valuables stolen from the antiques collector are hidden close to the ruins located at the western river bank near where the river joins the lake. You must take these valuables and bring them to the Last Shelter.
#subobj  1
New guards' barracks
New barracks for the guards have been built on the western bank where the river makes a loop. To reach the place where the collector's items is hidden you must go past the barracks.
#subobj  2
Find the stuff
The collector's things are hidden in the ruins on the western river bank near the place where it flows into the lake.
#subobj  3
Take the collector's things
You must take the collector's things and bring them to the Last Shelter.
